716365f-a.text:
Amsterdam Avenue, north from 184th street. The frame houses on the S.W. corner of 185th Street were built around 1895. From 186th to 187th streets, on the west side, stands the new Yeshiva College of America, dedicated December 1928.

November 3, 1934.

P.L.Sperr, Photographer.
